Trong khi do doanh thu ban hang truc tuyen cua E-mart vao Viet Nam nam 2012 cung len toi 89 trieu USD.E-mart cho biet dang gap rut trien khai hoat dong mo chi nhanh dau tien tai Viet Nam trong nam 2013 va muc tieu den nam 2017 se dua vao hoat dong 17 sieu thi.Danh gia ve su co mat cua cac san pham Viet Nam tai Han Quoc ong Cho Giam doc E-mart nhan dinh `` van chua tuong xung voi tiem nang ma thi truong Viet co the cung cap ''
